{"tid":1432029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「適合用作傷害他人物品」 違犯《香港人權法案條例》","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:54.000Z","uid":144497,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e745c840a24d8d2a081d1fbce6f5627e4b74b7","tid":1432029,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2617363834962271&amp;id=1109610452404291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2617363834962271%26id%3D1109610452404291&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO79lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=0c4586f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2617363834962271&amp;id=1109610452404291</a><br />\n<br />\n【警方的法律理據】<br />\n尋晚有網民發起觀星集會，用觀星筆苦中作樂，不過同日警方嘅例行記者會上，有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華重申，以「適合用作傷害他人物品」呢個理由做法律理據，去定性雷射筆係攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n我地翻查法庭文件，發現係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1994年 R v. Chong Ah-Choi 案件中</span></span>，時任包致金大法官認為，由於<span style=\"color: red;\">「適合用作傷害他人物品」當中嘅「適合」定義太廣闊</span>，已經裁定呢項理據係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>違犯《香港人權法案條例》</strong></span>，以後都唔可以再被用作定罪基礎。<br />\n<br />\n但係警方一直堅持用呢個做理由，係咪錯誤理解法律？<br />\n係唔係警方明明知道，但係又去用一條違犯人權法既法律理據去拉人呢? <br />\n<br />\n#警方話如覺得做法恰當_無需要諮詢律政司<br />\n#咁樣對當事人不公_影響法庭審訊喎<br />\n#警方嘅法律理據何在<br />\n#法治唔應該淪為政治工具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣組可以做野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3742452c68b89b2fd9cca47e81e1d1c1bd16326","tid":1432029,"uid":80777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54cf96609bbc0e5523cca52b30c00b4329530a14","tid":1432029,"uid":289124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fdf7cfd638584b51a34067f3516e63cecce1ea91","tid":1432029,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0